name: Trish (Patricia) Gooch
what_you_do: Tara LaFon Gooch is an award-winning leadership and TEDx speaker, CEO, thought leader, coach, and author specializing in the transformative power of confidence.
social_proof: Tara LaFon Gooch earned her MBA from the University of North Carolina at Wilmington as well as certificates in financial management and management from Cornell University and The University of Notre Dame - Mendoza College of Business, respectively.
